title: Meditation Secrets - Change Your Fate
description:
This is truly an amazing set of meditation and spiritual advice that you will find anywhere on the web.

The author of these works, Bill Bodri, has been taught under an enlightened Master, Master Nan-Huai Chin, and has given us his secrets for success in meditation from religious practices such as Buddhism, Taoism, and even Christianity.  

In this file you will find books that can help you improve in many areas of your life, from meditation to marital arts, to any aspect of your life.  

For real, his secrets have really helped me and they'll help you too if you give them a shot. Especially the CHANGE YOUR FORTUNE book.
